divs: Sighting DetailsI was in holidays, taking some photus, at that time i was not seeing anything strange, but then, after i pass the photo to the computer i saw 2 strange objects in the sky. I have show this picture to some people, and everybody tell me that this is strange. I have send the photo to a organizacion in Portugal that study this kind of phenomenus, but they told me that this is some kind of durty in the lents of my digital camera!!!! I did not believe it and i decide to send the photo to you to give me a second opinion about this photo. thks
